            + '<div class="pi-text">Different kinds of data just use different "rules" for turning those bits back into something meaningful: a number, a letter, the colour of one pixel, or the loudness of a sound at one instant. Learn to read and write binary and you\'ve learned the <strong>alphabet of computing</strong> — everything else is built on top of it.</div>'
