      how: 'Newer GCSE specifications — especially the 2025 WJEC (Wales) GCSE — ask <strong>what AI/machine learning is</strong>, <strong>where it is used</strong>, and its <strong>ethical, social and legal impact</strong> (bias, jobs, privacy, accountability).',
